          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1589292786632-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>saag aloo with peas</strong> in a bowl with the<strong> halved pitta </strong>to the side</p><p>Garnish with your<strong> nigella seeds</strong> and <strong>chilli rounds</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
